104
00:07:09,041 --> 00:07:12,041
MARGHERITA: NO, DON'T WORRY.
YOU DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.

105
00:07:20,083 --> 00:07:26,166
I DON'T UNDERSTAND ANYTHING ANYMORE

106
00:07:26,250 --> 00:07:27,791
[faucet running]

107
00:07:30,125 --> 00:07:36,833
ANDREA: DO YOU WANT TO HANG OUT AGAIN?

108
00:07:36,916 --> 00:07:38,541
[dramatic music playing]

109
00:07:59,333 --> 00:08:01,333
[groans, sighs]

110
00:08:02,083 --> 00:08:03,125
[cell phone clicks]

111
00:08:13,666 --> 00:08:14,666
[cell phone clicks]

112
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,583
[indistinct chatter]

113
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:45,958
[Carlo] Good morning!

114
00:08:49,833 --> 00:08:51,458
[tense music playing]

115
00:09:11,791 --> 00:09:15,208
"ALL LITERATURE IS AN ASSAULT
ON THE FRONTIER." FRANZ KAFKA

116
00:09:27,791 --> 00:09:29,541
