117
00:09:42,791 --> 00:09:45,458
You wanted all of this. Now it's yours.

118
00:09:49,291 --> 00:09:51,291
[water bubbling]

119
00:10:00,791 --> 00:10:01,916
[groans]

120
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,666
- [exhales]
- [packing tape tearing]

121
